<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Irreplaceable friends (Emil)</span></p>
<p class="para">I had given up on everything.
<br>An unjust world that pours everything down on me.
<br>A magical weapon. Cursed Eyes. Eternal life.
<br>A dark old mansion. My big sister, sealed away.
<br>That’s when they arrived.
<br>Vulgar, violent, and pushy.
<br>But in their own way...also kind.
<br>They told me I had a reason to live.
<br>They told me I couldn’t just die.
<br>They showed me the light.
<br><br>
And so, I… I have to live.
<br>For the sake of those who fought with me.
<br>No matter what.</p>
