<p class="title"><span class="title-box">A lie hidden in a castle for a thousand years (Shadowlord)</span></p>
<p class="para">There is no luxury of choice. If Yonah can be saved, it doesn’t matter if i have to wander the wastes of time for eternity. Even if… Even if our promise was a lie.</p>
