<p class="title"><span class="title-box">A scene from the journey’s end (Kainé)</span></p>
<p class="para">Hey, Emil. Sure it could be that everything we’ve done means squat.
<br>But even so…
<br>I treasure the time we all spent together more than anything else in the world.
<br>You feel the same way, right? So...don’t cry.
<br>Keep your chin up.
<br>Smile.
<br>I’m sure that...he’d tell you to do the same.</p>
