<p class="title"><span class="title-box">There you were, in a paradise of scrap metal (City Ruins)</span></p>
<p class="para">In an almost unbelievably far-flung future.
<br>Machines fought against weapon-wielding puppets.
<br>Even after those who ordered them to war had died out, never once did they forget what they were told.
<br>Like an abandoned child.
<br>This is the story of souls with life.</p>
