<p class="title"><span class="title-box">That which I truly desired (A Beautiful Song)</span></p>
<p class="para">He was far beyond the repulsive thing I am.
<br>Yet I couldn’t completely give up on him.
<br>If even these thoughts are a crime, then… please.
<br>Kill me. I don’t care if I lose everything.
<br>I truly love him.
<br>So please…
<br>Don’t ignore me…</p>
